y, and with a diverse readership from both sides of the Atlantic in mind.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aLaw -- International and Comparative Law. 4aPhilosophy -- Political Philosophy. 7aLAW / International.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476760640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804767606423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804767606/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles